{
  "stem": "11882.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then we went on to Nuremberg in a command car, which is a big thing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't know, 18th, 19th of October.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Ice cold, the wind blew in on us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We froze, but we made it to Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then they put us up in the Grand Hotel Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Hitler's hotel in Nuremberg, where he had his big party meetings, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And now it was ours.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the rest of the city was a mess.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You would see the bathtubs sticking out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Well, you know, these war pipes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the city was just a mass of graveyards of these bombed out Nurembergers, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We'd take Sunday walks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You wouldn't see a soul.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I learned later-- I learned a few years back, Dr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Kempner and myself-- I was taken along as his helper, were the guests of the city of Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And at that time, Nuremberg-- greatly loved Nuremberg Burgermeister told us that 70% of the Nurembergers never returned.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They went out and settled somewhere else, and other people came into Nuremberg, you know, refugees from Poland, Czechoslovakia, all over.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And 70% of the real genuine Nurembergers never came back to their city.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like everyone else, they had just been dislocated by this earthquake, the war, and just settled down wherever they landed and built themselves a little life wherever they were, you know?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in Nuremberg, we were sort of kept under guard all the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And also-- didn't-- weren't allowed to mingle in any way with the native people, insofar as they were there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What was your job now in Nuremberg?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Your responsibilities.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was what they call a research analyst.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was supposedly knew German and English, a rare thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Germans didn't know English, the English didn't know German, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
